body:
I’m so, so sorry…

I’m so sorry that I’m not really posting anymore here… Real life has caught up on me - but it’s not a bad thing! Actually I’m having my first baby come september. A little girl! So yeah, my mind has been elsewhere and will be for quite a while. If I get the time, I’ll start posting here again. I’m still a huge fan of DT and I’ll sure teach my daughter to love him too ;-)
